{
  "stem": "1753.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 126.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The total population may have been 4,000 of-- of that little city, but there may have been as many as 500 Jewish people in that town.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there were a lot of Jewish children, so they sent me there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's where-- incidentally, where I was bar mitzvahed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my parents came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not in particular.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was so engrossed in being with a number of other Jewish young people there in that little town.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because in-- in that village, where I lived before, there-- it was not a very pleasant surrounding, especially when Hitler came to power.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I sure did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- it was certainly tremendously different, because I had a chance to be involved with more Jewish families, which was not possible.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before I left where?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Incidentally, my comments that I made to you before we went on camera, is that I was bar mitzvahed in 1936.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Actually, I was bar mitzvahed in 1938.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I left that little village and subsequently went to that small town, where the larger Jewish family-- families were.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was in-- that-- that was in 1936.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And yes, by all means, I remember quite a bit of anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, I remember precisely the day-- the exact day-- which was January 1930, when Hitler was elected to power, became chancellor of the German Reich.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was January 30, 1930.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Unless I am utterly wrong, but I believe that was the date.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or maybe it was in 1933.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You might be correct.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think it was 1933.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Let me correct myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was January 30, 1933.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The reason I do remember, because Hitler's regime lasted for exactly 12 years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was January 30th, 1933.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I want to make sure the date is correct.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
